text: Sven Nordenström (9 December 1888 - 2 May 1945) was a Swedish fencer. He competed in the individual sabre event at the 1912 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1888 births Category:1945 deaths Category:Swedish male fencers Category:Swedish sabre fencers Category:Olympic fencers of Sweden Category:Fencers at the 1912 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Stockholm
